data.description: This charming 5 bedroom, 3.5 bathroom home with a full finished basement is ready for your enjoyment.  Kitchen has lots of cabinets with new granite counter tops, sink & faucet, newer microwave, stove and refrigerator, a large pantry and new lvt flooring. Screen porch off the family room is perfect for morning coffee or an evening of relaxation. First floor office allows lots of natural light and French doors for privacy.  2nd floor laundry room includes 2023 washer & dryer. Fully finished walk-out basement has plenty of natural light and recessed lighting, a large family room, kitchenette, bedroom, a full bath and storage room. The basement family room offers a French door that opens to a covered patio and don't miss the 2nd laundry room located in the basement storage room.  The landscaping remains lush with 4-sides irrigation.  Both hvac's newer. Beautiful move-in condition. Quarterly dues include pool and playground.
